<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Verify Your Email Address</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #B91C1C;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .code-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border: 3px solid #B91C1C;
        }

        .code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 10px;
            color: #B91C1C;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: #e0f2fe;
            border: 1px solid #7dd3fc;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚úâÔ∏è Verify Your Email</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome to Art Gallery!</h2>

            <p>Thank you for signing up. To complete your registration, please verify your email address using the code below:</p>

            <div class="code-box">
                <h3>Verification Code:</h3>
                <div class="code">
                    <%= code %>
                </div>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #666;">Enter this code on the verification page</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong>üìã Important Information:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>This code will expire in 10 minutes</li>
                    <li>This code can only be used once</li>
                    <li>If you didn't create an account, you can safely ignore this email</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>Once verified, you'll have full access to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Browse and purchase beautiful artworks</li>
                <li>Save your favorite pieces</li>
                <li>Track your orders</li>
                <li>Connect with artists</li>
            </ul>

            <p>This verification email was sent to <strong><%= email %></strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Art Gallery Team</p>
            <p>If you didn't sign up for Art Gallery, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
